title: Philip Chapman - Precious Love [FLAC]
description:
Light and spacious strings, keyboards and ethereal voices float in the air like perfume, calming the mind and producing a state of deep serenity and reflective reverie. A consistent mood of tranquility and peace permeates the senses, infusing an optimistic impression and clear awareness of all that is precious on our planet. Whether used for relaxation or as a quiet background landscape, this is the music to rest you, to balance, recharge and re-inspire you.
